# Ram_Cleaner

**Cross-Platform RAM Cleaner & Monitor**  
Automatically monitors memory usage and triggers a cleanup when usage exceeds a threshold. Works on Windows, Linux, and macOS.

## Features

- Detects operating system and applies the correct memory-cleaning strategy.
- Configurable threshold, intervals, and one-time test mode via CLI flags.
- Logs before/after memory usage for evidence and debugging.
- Cross-platform startup integration: Task Scheduler, systemd, launchd.

## Quick Start

```bash
git clone https://github.com/soumamukherjee27/Ram_Cleaner-Win11-Linux-Mac-OS.git
cd Ram_Cleaner-Win11-Linux-Mac-OS
pip install -r requirements.txt
python ram_cleaner.py --once --verbose            # Run once for testing
python ram_cleaner.py --threshold 60              # Run indefinitely
